{
  "text": "Unless C is a very small set, it is necessary to restrict P{C\\C) to a parametric family of distributions to make equation (1) useful in applications. The dogit model of [CITATION_1] and the random-constraint models of Swait and Ben-Akiva (1987a) are examples of how this can be done.",
